verbose_text: Among these, miR-661, miR-523-3p, miR-200c-3p and miR-141-3p were significantly differentially expressed, while the other miRNAs were moderately differentially expressed; the majority of these miRNAs are related to obesity (miR-143-3p, miR-221-3p, miR-125a-5p, miR-16-5p and cancer (miR-141-3p, miR-181a-5p, miR-18a-5p, miR-30a-3p).
evidence: miR-200c-3p and miR-141-3p were significantly differentially expressed
